00:40:59,356 --> 00:41:02,291
and everything that he might want me to do.

484
00:41:05,496 --> 00:41:09,227
To be perfectly honest,
I find that impulse understandable.

485
00:41:09,834 --> 00:41:13,702
I don't think I could do half of the things
that I said I could.

486
00:41:13,838 --> 00:41:16,932
I mean, you know, anatomically.

487
00:41:18,642 --> 00:41:21,475
Honey, what exactly did you say?

488
00:41:25,182 --> 00:41:26,979
I humiliated myself.

489
00:41:28,552 --> 00:41:29,917
Completely.

490
00:41:32,423 --> 00:41:33,822
I mean, do you...

491
00:41:35,793 --> 00:41:39,126
Do you understand that?
Do you know what I'm saying?

492
00:41:41,031 --> 00:41:42,123
Yes.

493
00:41:43,667 --> 00:41:48,229
I had to know
if there was a chance for me with Harris.

494
00:41:50,107 --> 00:41:51,904
