505
00:42:22,273 --> 00:42:25,003
No. No, he wouldn't. He's not...

506
00:42:26,977 --> 00:42:30,242
He's not the kind of person that would
recover from something like that.

507
00:42:31,682 --> 00:42:32,842
Lila?

508
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,947
Lila, dear, are you up?

509
00:42:35,019 --> 00:42:36,179
Just a minute, Mother.

